</div>
<div class="hero">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold underline">
     Cook to a playlist, <br>
     Not a timer!
  </h1>
  <div class = "button">
    <%= image_tag('Spotify_Icon_RGB_White.png', class: 'icon') %>
    <%= link_to 'Sign in with Spotify', '/auth/spotify', method: :post, class: "link-text"%>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="usp-container">
  <div class="img">
    <img class="recipe-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515516089376-88db1e26e9c0?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2940&q=80" alt="Recipe Image">
  </div>
  <div class="text">
    <h2 class="usp">As you cook, the playlist cooks right along with you.</h2>
    <p>With Jammaker you will never have to think about what music to listen to while cooking. <br> An online tool that makes it easy to create playlists that last exactly as long as the cooking time. Forget about your playlist having to stop mid-dinner, or worrying whether they will run out of songs by the time you cut the cheese.</p>
    <div class = "dark-btn">
      <%= image_tag('Spotify_Icon_RGB_White.png', class: 'icon') %>
      <%= link_to 'Sign in with Spotify', '/auth/spotify', method: :post, class: "link-text" %>
    </div>
 </div>
</div>

